riddle for you.

20:31.400 --> 20:32.300
All right.

20:32.700 --> 20:36.100
What has multiple
orgasms and hums?

20:37.000 --> 20:38.000
I give up.

20:47.000 --> 20:48.400
Come on, I'll show you.

20:51.200 --> 20:52.000
Alan...

20:52.800 --> 20:53.700
Alan, I'm leaving.

